   LOCKS & KEYS

   Locks and keys are a physical control system used for protecting
   installations, personnel and property.  We have experienced personnel
   to maintain a proprietary lock and key system for your facility.  This
   covers the management of you lock codes, key production, positive key
   control, changing of lock cores and safe combinations.  Control of your
   locks and keys is one of the easiest and most inexpensive ways to
   secure your work areas.

   For more information, please contact Lou Widawski at 202-366-1798, or
   our main office at 202-366-4677, between the hours of 9 AM & 5:30 PM.


